OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing
OL,5,Cteenager
OL,7,FA murder investigation has been
OL,8,Flaunched after police discovered a
OL,9,Fbody in a park near Ebbw Vale.
OL,11,FThe family of a 14-year-old girl,
OL,12,Fnamed only as Lilly by Gwent Police,
OL,13,Fhave been informed.
OL,15,FLilly had previously been reported
OL,16,Fmissing, last seen on Saturday evening.
OL,18,FFormal identification is yet to take
OL,19,Fplace.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
