OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing
OL,5,Cteenager
OL,7,FThe body was discovered in the Duffryn
OL,8,FPark area of Blaina on Monday 22 June,
OL,9,Fjust after 10pm.
OL,11,FSenior Investigating Officer,
OL,12,FDetective Chief Inspector Steven
OL,13,FThomas said:
OL,15,F"We understand that this will cause
OL,16,Fdistress and concern amongst our
OL,17,Fcommunities.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
