OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1782238703
OL,3,CMurder investigation launched after
OL,4,Cbody found in search for missing
OL,5,Cteenager
OL,7,F"We have a large police presence in
OL,8,Fthe area at this time as enquiries are
OL,9,Fongoing to establish the circumstances
OL,10,Fof the death. Our officers are here
OL,11,Fand available for you to speak to.
OL,13,F"We encourage anyone with information
OL,14,Fto please speak with us or you can
OL,15,Fcontact us on the usual channels."
